          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You can use this enumeration to choose a predefined size for elements in a button. The value you choose for button size can be effectively overridden by explicitly assigning values for configuration elements like padding, corner style, or title and subtitle font sizes."
